      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh okay i get it. if not the cipro then what? like if i just wanted to take something for the pressure and congestion so i can actually sleep tonight, is it safe to take Sudafed (pseudoephedrine)? i've heard it's pretty standard for sinus stuff and i just need something that actually works since the saline isnt doing anything.",
